This week, the world lost my great aunt Pat, who was basically a third grandma to me.☀️ I debated whether I should post about her right after a bikini thirst trap, but as she liked to remind me: “Jasmine, you’ll always look hot cuz you look just like me!”
There are no words to explain how it felt to have her light shed on you. Please be patient while I never get over this. ❤️🍔
